div.bibl: The Philippine Messenger, Vol. II, No. 15, Sept. 1935FILIPINO DANCE WAS A GREAT SUCCESS

body.p: A large crowd attended the Filipino Press Dance at the Majestic Hotel Sky Ballroom, Sunday, Aug. 25th. Miss Emma Jones was chosen Queen and Vida Elliot, Princess. Trophies were given to winners of different events. It was a colorful evening. The Luzonian Orchestra played for the dancers.
